530
00:35:13,727 --> 00:35:15,854
This case would be a headache
even for him.

531
00:35:17,481 --> 00:35:18,816
All right.

532
00:35:18,899 --> 00:35:22,861
I should curry favor with our future
judges, prosecutors, and lawyers.

533
00:35:22,945 --> 00:35:24,530
Here, have some. Take a break.

