00:36:07,406 --> 00:36:08,407
You don't care?

547
00:36:13,745 --> 00:36:14,830
What do you mean?

548
00:36:15,455 --> 00:36:17,082
The immediate cause is unknown.

549
00:36:18,542 --> 00:36:19,710
I really don't care.

