is not if he switched the glasses,

578
00:38:07,985 --> 00:38:10,487
but if he pushed Seo
on purpose or accidentally.

579
00:38:14,074 --> 00:38:16,076
<i>Answer my question.</i>

580
00:38:16,868 --> 00:38:18,870
<i>He tried to stop me</i>
<i>from calling the police,</i>

581
00:38:18,954 --> 00:38:21,248
then he tripped
and rolled down the stairs.

582
00:38:21,331 --> 00:38:23,417
Hey, why are you telling us this just now?

583
00:38:23,500 --> 00:38:25,627
