not just medical examiners?

603
00:39:54,888 --> 00:39:58,058
Everyone says it's not easy
to pick one as the cause of death.

604
00:39:58,141 --> 00:39:59,893
Jeez, what a mess.

605
00:39:59,976 --> 00:40:01,353
Without the second autopsy…

606
00:40:03,438 --> 00:40:06,858
There's a renowned American
forensic pathologist named Johns Patrol.

607
00:40:06,942 --> 00:40:08,402
I'll contact him for help.

608
00:40:09,653 --> 00:40:11,196
Why can't we figure out the cause?

609
00:40:12,197 --> 00:40:13,949
What if we lose both of them?

610
00:40:14,699 --> 00:40:15,826
That won't happen.

611
00:40:16,910 --> 00:40:18,161
PROSECUTORS' OFFICE

612
00:40:20,956 --> 00:40:22,332
I hope that's the case too.

613
00:40:23,208 --> 00:40:24,751
HEAD PROSECUTOR JIN HYEONG-U SUED

614
00:40:25,419 --> 00:40:26,670
I saw it too.

615
00:40:31,883 --> 00:40:33,760
Have you interviewed the accused yet?

616
00:40:37,556 --> 00:40:39,599
You seem to be doing great.

617
00:40:41,184 --> 00:40:43,353
Investigate the case swiftly
and thoroughly.

618
00:40:44,521 --> 00:40:48,316
I hope you're curious as to why I'm here.

