a false defamatory statement.

701
00:45:35,770 --> 00:45:37,981
I don't understand why it's a fact.

702
00:45:38,064 --> 00:45:39,149
-Me neither.
-Totally.

703
00:45:39,232 --> 00:45:40,984
-I don't get it.
-It makes no sense!

704
00:45:41,067 --> 00:45:42,652
Why did you think he stated facts?

705
00:45:43,945 --> 00:45:47,157
At first, I also wrote that it was false
but changed my answer

706
00:45:47,824 --> 00:45:48,992
because of the comma.

707
00:45:49,075 --> 00:45:50,243
-Comma?
-Where?

708
00:45:50,827 --> 00:45:52,871
I noticed the comma between

709
00:45:52,954 --> 00:45:55,540
